-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

btguru Torrent Scraper is a collection of php classes and scripts that allow you to search indexes for downloads that have a common pattern in their name. You can search automatically for new releases by your favorite group, and program in quite a few different parameters.


The default packaging for btguru includes a search engine, and abstract search class with an example of a scraper that works bt.etree.org. You can also create a wanted list, and have the system obtain new releases automatically for you.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Dependencies:

	php5-cli
	php5-curl

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Please check the FAQ for btguru scraper at www.gurudigitalsolutions.com/btguru, or visit our forums at www.gurudigitalsolutions.com/gforum for more information.
